line_1: But still on Julia vainly called,
line_2: With desperate words that breast appalled.

line_1: And Babylon the spacious city call'd;
line_2: Old Babel next with boundless cost she wall'd;

line_1: Of Vanity the Mirror This was call'd.
line_2: At his dull Desk, amid his Legers stall'd,

line_1: The drooping Muses then he westward call'd,
line_2: What Time the Turk th'enfeebled Grecian thrall'd;

line_1: Whilst life remains, (if life it can be call'd
line_2: T' exist in fleshly bondage thus enthrall'd)
